Body: Description: When scheduling a Host Discovery, with setting to run Host Inventory when discovery completes.  The Host Inventory will refresh if you kick the discovery manually but does not run when the discovery is run through the schedule
What We've Learned Updated: Customer upgraded to NEA v11.6.0.138
Next Steps Updated: Awaiting confirmation that the issue is resolved

Steps to Reproduce Updated: 1. Configure Host Discovery
2. Schedule Host Discovery
3. Kick off Host Discovery from schedule
4. Nothing happens
